    "{{accountName}} bank sync settings": "{{accountName}} 银行同步设置",
    "<0><0>How is cash flow calculated?</0></0><1>Cash flow shows the balance of your budgeted accounts over time, and the amount of expenses/income each day or month. Your budgeted accounts are considered to be \"cash on hand,\" so this gives you a picture of how available money fluctuates.</1>": "<0><0>现金流量是怎么计算的？</0></0><1>现金流量显示预算账户在一段时间内的余额，以及每天或每月的支出/收入金额。您的预算账户被视为 “手头现金”，因此这可以让您了解可用资金的波动情况。</1>",
    "<0>Authentication method</0> modifies how users log in to the system.": "<0>验证方式</0>会指定用户如何登录系统。",
    "<0>Balance:</0><1>{{amount}}</1>": "<0>余额：</0><1>{{amount}}</1>",
    "<0>Budgeted:</0><1>{{amount}}</1>": "<0>已预算数额：</0><1>{{amount}}</1>",
    "<0>Envelope budgeting</0> (recommended) digitally mimics physical envelope budgeting system by allocating funds into virtual envelopes for different expenses. It helps track spending and ensure you don't overspend in any category.": "<0>信封预算系统</0>（推荐） 通过使用虚拟信封把资金分配到不同的支出，以模拟实体信封预算系统。它有助于追踪你的开销之处，确保您不会在任何类别中超支。",
    "<0>Goal Type:</0><1>{{type}}</1>": "<0>目标类型:</0><1>{{type}}></1>",
    "<0>Goal:</0><1>{{amount}}</1>": "<0>目标数目：</0><1>{{amount}}</1>",
    "{{categoryGroupName}} expense group categories": "{{categoryGroupName}} 消费组别",
    "{{scheduleName}} is due {{distanceFromNow}} ({{formattedDate}})": "{{scheduleName}}在{{distanceFromNow}}内到期({{formattedDate}}])",
    "{{status}} (Split)": "{{status}} (拆分)",
    "<0>{{category}}</0> is used by existing transactions or it has a positive leftover balance currently.": "<0>{{category}}</0> 已有交易在使用，或当前有正余额。",
    "<0>{{category}}</0> is used by existing transactions.": "<0>{{category}}</0> 正在被已有交易使用。",
    "<0><0>Custom Report:</0></0> <2>{{name}}</2>": "<0><0>自定义报表：</0></0> <2>{{name}}</2>",
    "<0><0>How are \"Average\" and \"Spent Average MTD\" calculated?</0></0><1>They are both the average cumulative spending by day for the three months before the selected \"compare\" month.</1>": "<0><0>“平均支出”和“本月至今平均支出”是如何计算的？</0></0><1>它们都是所选 “比较 ”月份之前三个月按天计算的平均累计支出</1>",
    "<0>Actual's data directory</0> <2><0>where your files are stored</0></2>": "<0>Actual 的资料存档</0> <2><0>你文档的收集之处</0></2>",
    "<0>Actual</0> is a super fast privacy-focused app for managing your finances.": "<0>Actual</0> 是一款极速、注重隐私的个人财务管理应用。",
    "<0>Are you sure you want to delete it?</0> If so, you must select another category to transfer existing transactions and balance to.": "<0>您确定删除它吗?</0> 如果是，您必须选择另一个类别来转移现有交易和余额。",
    "<0>End-to-end encryption</0> is not available when making an unencrypted connection to a remote server. You'll need to enable HTTPS on your server to use end-to-end encryption. This problem may also occur if your browser is too old to work with Actual.": "<0>端到端加密</0>在未加密连接到远程服务器时不可用。您需要在服务器上启用HTTPS才能使用端到端加密。如果您的浏览器版本过旧无法兼容Actual，也可能出现此问题。",
    "<0>End-to-end encryption</0> is not available when running without a server. Budget files are always kept unencrypted locally, and encryption is only applied when sending data to a server.": "<0>端到端加密</0> 在无服务器运行时不可用。 预算文件在本地始终以未加密形式保存，仅当数据发送至服务器时才会启用加密。",
    "<0>End-to-end encryption</0> is not enabled. Any data on the server is still protected by the server password, but it's not end-to-end encrypted which means the server owners have the ability to read it. If you want, you can use an additional password to encrypt your data on the server.": "<0>端到端加密</0>未启用。服务器上的数据仍受服务器密码保护，但未经端到端加密意味着服务器所有者可读取这些数据。如需您想增强保护，您可为服务器数据设置额外加密密码。",
    "<0>Experimental features.</0> These features are not fully tested and may not work as expected. THEY MAY CAUSE IRRECOVERABLE DATA LOSS. They may do nothing at all. Only enable them if you know what you are doing.": "<0>实验性功能。</0>这些功能尚未经过完整测试，可能无法按预期运行。可能导致无法恢复的数据丢失，甚至可能完全无效。除非您完全了解潜在风险，否则请勿启用。",
    "<0>Budget ID:</0> {{budgetId}}": "<0>预算 ID:</0> {{budgetId}}",
    "<0>Language</0> is the display language of all text. Please note that no warranty is provided for the accuracy or completeness of non-English translations. If you encounter a translation error, feel free to make a suggestion on <3>Weblate</3>.": "<0>语言</0>是应用的显示语言。温馨提示：非英文的翻译的准确性或完整性不含保证。如果您遇到翻译错误，请随时在<3>Weblate</3>提出建议。",
    "<0>Language</0> support is not available. Please follow the instructions <3>here</3> to add missing translation files.": "暂时无<0>语言</0>支持。请根据<3>此处</3>的说明添加缺失的翻译文件。",
    "<0>No server configured</0>": "<0>未配置服务器</0>",
    "<0>Reset budget cache</0> will clear all cached values for the budget and recalculate the entire budget. All values in the budget are cached for performance reasons, and if there is a bug in the cache you won't see correct values. There is no danger in resetting the cache. Hopefully you never have to do this.": "<0>重置预算缓存</0>将会清除预算里所有的缓存值而重新计算整个预算表。所有预算中的数值都会因为性能原因而被缓存。如果缓存中有错误，您将看不到正确的数值。重置缓存是没有危险的。希望你永远不需这么做。",
    "$10 a week": "每周＄10",
    "$10 a week, up to a maximum of $80": "每周＄10，最高限定为＄80",
    "$50 each month": "每月＄50",
