    "Account": "账户",
    "Account list": "账户列表",
    "<0>Export</0> your data as a zip file containing <3>db.sqlite</3> and <5>metadata.json</5> files. It can be imported into another Actual instance by closing an open file (if any), then clicking the \"Import file\" button, then choosing \"Actual.\"": "<0>导出数据</0>您的数据为包含<3>db.sqlite</3>和<5>metadata.json</5>文件的压缩包。如需将数据导入其他Actual实例，请先关闭已打开的文件（如有），然后点击\"导入文件\"按钮，并选择\"Actual\"选项。",
    "<0>Formatting</0> does not affect how budget data is stored, and can be changed at any time.": "<0>格式设置</0>不会改变预算资料如何被收存，何时可以更改。",
    "<0>IDs</0> are the names Actual uses to identify your budget internally. There are several different IDs associated with your budget. The Budget ID is used to identify your budget file. The Sync ID is used to access the budget on the server.": "<0>ID标识符</0>是Actual内部用于识别您的预算的唯一名称。您的预算关联着多个不同的ID标识符：预算ID用于标识预算文件，同步ID则用于访问服务器上的预算数据。",
    "<0>Important:</0> if you forget this password <3>and</3> you don't have any local copies of your data, you will lose access to all your data. The data cannot be decrypted without the password.": "<0>重要提示：</0>如果您忘记此密码<3>且</3>未保留任何本地数据副本，您将永久失去所有数据的访问权限。没有密码将无法解密数据。",
    "<0>Link a <1>European</1> bank account</0> to automatically download transactions. GoCardless provides reliable, up-to-date information from hundreds of banks.": "<0>关联<1>欧洲</1> 银行账户<0>, 以便自动下载交易。 GoCardless提供了来自数百家银行的可靠的最新信息.",
    "{{categoryName}} shortcuts": "{{categoryName}} 快捷方式",
    "{{count}} uncategorized transactions_other": "{{count}} 未分类交易",
    "<0>Category Learning</0> will automatically determine the best category for a transaction and create a rule that sets the category for the payee. <3>Learn more</3>": "<0>类别学习</0>会主动选择对一条交易最适合的组别以及 create a rule that sets the category for the payee. <3>更多详情</3>",
    "<0>Create a local account</0> if you want to add transactions manually. You can also <3>import QIF/OFX/QFX files into a local account</3>.": "<0>创建本地账户</0>，如果你想手动添加交易。你也可以<3>将 QIF/OFX/QFX 文件导入本地账户</3>。",
    "<0>Link a <1>Brazilian</1> bank account</0> to automatically download transactions. Pluggy.ai provides reliable, up-to-date information from hundreds of banks.": "<0>链接一个 <1>巴西</1>银行账户</0>，以自动下载交易记录。Pluggy.ai 可从数百家银行提供可靠、最新的信息。",
    "<0>Link a <1>North American</1> bank account</0> to automatically download transactions. SimpleFIN provides reliable, up-to-date information from hundreds of banks.": "<0>链接一个 <1>北美</1>银行账户</0>，以自动下载交易记录。SimpleFIN 可从数百家银行提供可靠、最新的信息。",
    "<0>Read here</0> for instructions on how to migrate your data from YNAB. You need to export your data as JSON, and that page explains how to do that.": "<0>点击这里阅读</0>，了解如何从 YNAB 迁移数据。你需要将数据导出为 JSON 格式，该页面会说明如何操作。",
    "<0>Reset sync</0> is only available when syncing is enabled.": "仅在启用同步时，<0>重置同步</0> 功能才可用。",
    "<0>Reset sync</0> will remove all local data used to track changes for syncing, and create a fresh sync ID on the server. This file on other devices will have to be re-downloaded to use the new sync ID. Use this if there is a problem with syncing and you want to start fresh.": "<0>重置同步</0> 将移除所有用于同步变更追踪的本地数据，并在服务器上创建一个新的同步 ID。其他设备上的此文件将需要重新下载以使用新的同步 ID。如果同步出现问题且你希望重新开始，请使用此功能。",
    "<0>Server self-signed certificate</0> <2><0>enables a secure connection</0></2>": "<0>服务器自签名证书</0> <2><0>用于启用安全连接</0></2>",
    "<0>Sync ID:</0> {{syncId}}": "<0>同步 ID：</0>{{syncId}}",
    "<0>Themes</0> change the user interface colors.": "<0>主题</0> 可更改用户界面的配色。",
    "<allocatedAmount /> <italic>of <totalAmount /></italic>": "<allocatedAmount /> <italic>共 <totalAmount /></italic>",
    "A file with id \"{{id}}\" already exists with the name \"{{name}}\". This file will be replaced. This probably happened because files were manually moved around outside of Actual.": "ID 为 “{{id}}” 的文件已存在，文件名为 “{{name}}”。该文件将被替换。此情况很可能是由于在 Actual 之外手动移动了文件所致。",
    "A new version of Actual is available!": "有可用的 Actual 新版本！",
    "A new version of Actual is available! Your Pikapods instance will be automatically updated in the next few days - no action needed.": "Actual 有新版本可用！你的 Pikapods 实例将在接下来的几天内自动更新，无需手动操作。",
