    "{isSearching\n                        ? 'No matching shortcuts'\n                        : isInCategory\n                          ? 'No shortcuts in this category'\n                          : 'No matching shortcuts'}": "{isSearching\n                        ? '没有匹配的快捷方式'\n                        : 在分类中\n                          ? '此分类暂无快捷方式'\n                          : '没有匹配的快捷方式'}",
    "Actual is a personal finance tool that focuses on beautiful design and a slick user experience. <2>Editing your data should be as fast as possible.</2> On top of that, we want to provide powerful tools to allow you to do whatever you want with your data.": "Actual 是一款专注于优雅设计与流畅用户体验的个人财务工具。<2>编辑你的数据应当尽可能快速。</2>此外，我们还希望提供强大的工具，助你自由掌控和处理自己的财务数据。",
    "Actual is a super fast privacy-focused app for managing your finances. To secure your data, you'll need to set a password for your server.": "Actual 是一款极速且注重隐私的理财应用。为保障你的数据安全，你需要为服务器设置密码。",
    "Add a fixed percentage of your income to this category each month. You can choose to take the percentage from the current month or the previous month.": "每月按你收入的一定比例为此类别分配资金，可选择以本月或上月收入为基准。",
    "Add action": "添加操作",
    "<0>Move schedule </0><1></1><2> {{beforeOrAfter}} weekend</2>": "<0>使预定设在</0><1></1><2>周末 {{beforeOrAfter}}</2>",
    "Actual has updated the syncing format": "Actual 已更改同步格式",
    "Actual's data directory successfully changed.": "Actual 的数据目录已成功更改。",
    "Add": "添加",
    "Add account": "添加账户",
    "Actions": "活动",
    "Add another split": "添加另一拆分项",
    "Add enough to this category to cover the selected schedule. If the schedule occurs multiple times in a month, an amount will be added for each occurrence. You can choose to save up for the next occurrence over time (e.g. save $100 each month for a $300 quarterly bill) or cover each occurrence when it occurs (e.g. only add the $300 when the bill is due).": "为该类别添加足够的金额以覆盖所选的计划支出。如果该计划在一个月内发生多次，则每次都会添加相应金额。您可以选择提前分期存钱以备下次支出（例如，每月储蓄 $100 来支付每季度 $300 的账单），或在每次账单到期时再添加所需金额（例如，仅在账单到期时添加 $300）。",
    "Add entry": "添加记录",
    "Add condition": "添加条件",
    "Add group": "添加组别",
    "{{count}} payees_other": "{{count}} 收款人",
    "<0>Currency settings</0> affect how amounts are displayed throughout the application. Changing the currency will affect the number format, symbol position, and whether fractions are shown. These can be adjusted after the currency is set.": "<0>货币设置</0> 会影响应用中金额的显示方式。更改货币将影响数字格式、符号位置以及是否显示小数部分。在设定货币后，这些选项仍可进行调整。",
    "Add new rule": "添加新规则",
    "Actual field": "实际支出字段",
    "Actual requires access to <1>SharedArrayBuffer</1> in order to function properly. If you're seeing this error, either your browser does not support <3>SharedArrayBuffer</3>, or your server is not sending the appropriate headers, or you are not using HTTPS. See <6>our troubleshooting documentation</6> to learn more. <9></9>": "Actual 需要访问 <1>SharedArrayBuffer</1> 才能正常运行。如果您看到此错误，则您的浏览器不支持 <3>SharedArrayBuffer</3>，或者您的服务器没有发送适当的标头，或者您没有使用 HTTPS。有关详细信息，请参阅 <6> 我们的故障排除文档 </6>。<9></9>",
    "Actual uses <1>SharedArrayBuffer</1> to allow usage from multiple tabs at once and to ensure correct behavior when switching files. While it can run without access to<3>SharedArrayBuffer</3>, you may encounter data loss or notice multiple budget files being merged with each other.": "Actual 使用 <1>SharedArrayBuffer</1> 可以让多个标签页同时访问，并在切换文件时保持正确的行为。虽然在不使用<3>SharedArrayBuffer</3> 的的情况下程序依然能够运行，但可能会出现数据丢失，或者多个预算文件相互混合的情况。",
    "Add an amount to this category each month based on the values from previous months. For example, you can copy the amount from a year ago to budget for an annual expense, or budget the average of the last 3 months to account for seasonal changes.": "根据前几个月的数值，每月为该类别分配相应金额。例如，可参照一年前的数额以规划年度支出，或采用最近3个月的平均值以更好地反映季节性变化。",
