    "How past expenses are projected into the future.<1></1><2></2>Hampel Filtered Median: Filters out outliers before calculating the median expense.<4></4><5></5>Median: Uses the median of all historical expenses without filtering.<7></7><8></8>Mean: Uses the average of all historical expenses.": "如何根据过去支出预测未来？<1></1><2></2>Hampel滤波中位数：在计算中位支出前，先过滤掉异常值。<4></4><5></5>中位数：使用所有历史支出的中位数，不进行过滤。<7></7><8></8>平均值：使用所有历史支出的平均值。",
