    "If checked below, a rule will be created to do this rename while importing transactions.": "如果勾选下方选项，将在导入交易时创建一个规则来执行此重命名操作。",
    "If checked, the schedule will automatically create transactions for you in the specified account": "如果勾选，定期任务将会在指定账户中自动为您创建交易",
