    "If the automation UI isn't working for you, you can temporarily switch back to notes-based automations. Please let us know your feedback about what's not working on the <2>feedback issue</2>.": "如果自动化界面无法正常使用，您可以暂时切换回基于笔记的自动化功能。请在<2>反馈问题</2>中告知我们具体遇到的故障情况。",
