    "This is a <1>hosted file</1> but it was created by another user. You can only delete the local copy.": "这是一个<1>托管文件</1>，但它是由其他用户创建的。您只能删除本地副本。",
    "This is a <1>hosted file</1> which means it is stored on your server to make it available for download on any device. You can delete it from the server, which will also remove it from all of your devices.": "这是一个<1>托管文件</1>，意味着它存储在您的服务器上，以便在任何设备上下载。您可以将其从服务器中删除，删除后它也会从您所有的设备中移除。",
